defOutCompressVia(25.10)                              defOutCompressVia(25.10)

Name
       defOutCompressVia

Syntax
        defOutCompressVia {0 | 1}

       Type: Integer

       Default: 0

       Compresses the via statement in SPECIALNETS section. This variable con-
       trols  defOut  to  sort vias with two dimension array, so it can use DO
       numX BY numY STEP stepX stepY statement.

       The via array information is only preserved in the defIn  session,  but
       it will not be kept by saveDesign/restoreDesign.

Related Information
              * defIn

              * defOut

              * restoreDesign

              * saveDesign

